## Skill Routing

When the user's request matches a skill, invoke it:

- Test and fix bugs autonomously -> `/test-fix`
- Debug a specific issue, root cause analysis -> `/investigate`
- Save progress, end of session -> `/checkpoint`
- Start of session, full briefing -> `/recall`
- Quick health check -> `/status`
- Build/refresh knowledge base -> `/compile-wiki`
- Pre-landing code review -> `/review`
- Add a project rule -> `/rule`

